{"tid":2338216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小欖囚犯自製導電裝置遭調查 早前涉串謀爆炸還押","createTime":"2020-12-24T01:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T02:25:23.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"75f58664f0d4865a74c191abab6f084260d3e90f","tid":2338216,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNEatUu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNEatUu.jpg&h=1ccacb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懲教署表示，小欖精神病治療中心職員較早前接獲情報，指一名因「串謀導致相當可能會危害生命或財產的爆炸」而被還押的在囚人士，懷疑擅自拆除日間活動室物品及其個人鬚刨、收音機取出電線零件用作非法用途。管方隨即監視目標人物和地點，其後突擊搜查，在日間活動室搜出一批用途不明的自製非法物品，包括導電裝置及發熱線切割器等。該名在囚人士已被懲教署隔離接受調查，署方亦已將事件轉介警方跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201223/TIXXMIWXWZAMVJ4DVZZRW3KSNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201223%2FTIXXMIWXWZAMVJ4DVZZRW3KSNU%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MbHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=f887d190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201223%2FTIXXMIWXWZAMVJ4DVZZRW3KSNU%2F&h=874c9f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201223/TIXXMIWXWZAMVJ4DVZZRW3KSNU/</a>"},{"pid":"2ce650084f022f4ead4c8180904ee0703669e68a","tid":2338216,"uid":44171,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"監獄內可自制激光劍定磁力炮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如再作大D用電線制造中子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f3bd0be881a4c965d5bc41cf07a4f0f0a84327","tid":2338216,"uid":25260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:35:34.000Z","msg":"串謀爆炸係咩罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f10f74bcd10dfd4eef22ef3febac3a5f6154af2","tid":2338216,"uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ce650084f022f4ead4c8180904ee0703669e68a","tid":